<P>
Photo, Fred Zandpour of Cal State Fullerton's ad department says the tough job 
market "doesn't seem to be discouraging anyone." MIKE SERGIEF / For the Times; 
Photo, BECKA STAIR, Cal State Fullerton advertising major ; Photo, PAUL 
DELPIZZO, Cal State Fullerton advertising major 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
